error.message: Call to deprecated function module_load_include(). Deprecated in drupal:9.4.0 and is removed from drupal:11.0.0. Use Drupal::moduleHandler()->loadInclude($module, $type, $name = NULL). Note that including code from uninstalled extensions is no longer supported.
Value of core_version_requirement: ^8.8.0 || ^9.0 is not compatible with the next major version of Drupal core. See https://drupal.org/node/3070687.
Parse error in composer.json. Having a composer.json is not a requirement in general, but if there is one, it should be valid. See https://drupal.org/node/2514612.
